teacheasy.data

Class MultipleChoiceObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • teacheasy.data.PageObject
      • teacheasy.data.MultipleChoiceObject

  • public class MultipleChoiceObject
extends PageObject
    Encapsulates the data that describes a Multiple Choice Object as defined in the TeachEasy digital lesson XML format. Extends the page object supertype.
    Version:
    1.0 13 Feb 2015
    Author:
    Alistair Jewers

        Constructor to create the data object with the data parsed from XML.
        Parameters:
        nXStart - Relative X axis start position (0 - 1).
        nYStart - Relative Y axis start position (0 - 1).
        nOrientation - Orientation setting.
        nType - Type setting.
        nMarks - Marks awarded for a correct answer.
        nRetry - Retry setting.
